Class BKFAbstractType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwpf.model.types.BKFAbstractType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BookmarkFirstDescriptor 

    @Internal
public abstract class BKFAbstractType
extends java.lang.Object
    BooKmark First descriptor (BKF).

    Class and fields descriptions are quoted from Microsoft Office Word 97-2007 Binary File Format (.doc) Specification

    (BooKmark第一描述符（BKF）。类和字段描述引用自Microsoft Office Word 97-2007二进制文件格式（.Doc）规范)

      Get the bkf_flags field for the BKF record.(获取BKF记录的bkf_flags字段。)
      short getIbkl()
      Index to BKL entry in plcfbkl that describes the ending position of this bookmark in the CP stream.(plCFbkl中BKL条目的索引，该条目描述了此书签在CP流中的结束位置。)
      byte getItcFirst()
      When bkf.fCol==1, this is the index to the first column of a table column bookmark(当bkf.fCol==1时，这是表列书签第一列的索引)
      byte getItcLim()
      When bkf.fCol==1, this is the index to limit column of a table column bookmark(当bkf.fCol==1时，这是表列书签的限制列的索引)
      static int getSize()
      Size of record(记录大小)
      boolean isFCol()
      When 1, this bookmark marks a range of columns in a table specified by (bkf.itcFirst, bkf.itcLim)(当为1时，此书签标记由（bkf.itcFirst，bkf.itcLim）指定的表中的列范围)
      boolean isFPub()
      When 1, this indicates that this bookmark is marking the range of a Macintosh Publisher section(当为1时，表示此书签正在标记Macintosh Publisher部分的范围)
